@target vue3

A section showing how to install kun. Has id="install" for anchor linking.

content:
  heading: "Install"
  a code block showing: npm install -g @seyyidt/kun-js
  below: "Requires Node.js >= 20" in muted text

constraints:
  - use <script setup lang="ts">
  - scoped styles
  - code block should have a dark card background (#161616 or similar), rounded corners, monospace font, padding
  - slightly different background from main page to create visual separation (alternate section)
